[I noticed a couple of other places that needed a tweak to make sure
Disinterested Proposals don't receive any rewards.]

Amend Rule 955 by replacing the text:

                                                  and there were at
      least three votes in favor of the Proposal, then that Proposal
      is adopted.

with:

                                            and either there were at
      least three votes in favor of the Proposal or the Proposal was
      Disinterested, then that Proposal is adopted.

Amend Rule 947 by replacing the text:

      If a Proposal is adopted which

with:

      If an Interested Proposal is adopted which

Amend Rule 1786 by replacing the text:

      As soon as possible after a Proposal has been determined to
      have passed by the narrowest of margins,

with:

      As soon as possible after an Interested Proposal has been
      determined to have passed by the narrowest of margins,

[Comments:  Make sure Disinterested Proposals receive no rewards of any sort,
but make it possible to pass them with one vote.]


